enum_vars.name: DWAX_MASTERCODE_INIT
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the initialization.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_NVM_RESTORED
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the validation of reading from NVM the stored mastercode.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_START_WAIT_FOR_ARMING_REQUEST
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the waiting for arming request state to perform the arming request from DWAX lib component.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_START_GENERATE_PROCEDURE
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the generation procedure.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_START_SEED_GENERATION
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the request for random seed from CsmPi module.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_START_RANDOM_GENERATION
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the generation request for random number from CsmPi module.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_START_RANDOM_VERIFY
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the verifying if CsmPi generation of random number was complete in order to generate master code.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_GENERATE_MASTERCODE
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that is used to verify the storage of the MasterCode in NVM and generate MasterCode.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_WAITING_FOR_SAVE
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that starts the witing of saving the MasterCode.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_SAVE_MASTERCODE_VERIFY
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that is used to verify the storage of the MasterCode in NVM.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_MASTERCODE_GENERATED
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that is used to indicate the successful generation of MasterCode.

enum_vars.name: DWAX_MASTERCODE_SAFEFAIL
enum_vars.desc: MasterCode state that is used to indicate the safe fail of MasterCode.
